      "text": "Jurassic Park (Japanese: ジュラシック・パーク, Hepburn: Jurashikku Pāku) is a 1993 platform game developed and published by Sega for the Game Gear. Another version, with identical gameplay, was also released for the Master System only in Europe. The game is based on the 1993 film of the same name. It was praised for its graphics, but criticized for its short length and easy gameplay.",
